chapters.title: What Ever Happened to Murphy Brown?

description:
Murphy Brown was a favourite of mine when I was a kid. I grew up watching it as part of a block of syndicated sitcoms back in the 90’s, though it left syndication before I got to watch the last two seasons. For some reason I always remembered that vision of Murphy Brown coming in from the snow, whipping off the loose flakes as she flung her scarf off of her parka.

Rewatching this series was a lot of fun, and I hope some of that came across in this video. So many things ended up being cut from this video I could have easily added an extra 30 minutes to it. Maybe I’ll make it into a second video if this one does well enough/if enough people bother me about it.

The sources for this video were largely the series itself, but I owe a huge debt to the book Stealing the Show by Joy Press for some of the background info. There were a few other articles I found scattered through the internet, but this show is primarily my own reading.

I’ve got my next classic sitcom already lined up, waiting for a rewatch. It probably won’t be my next video, but there’s definitely another one of these coming. I hope everyone looks forward to it!
